metadata.name: Makaneki-Neko #1
metadata.description: ’Makaneki-Nekos is a community-based gaming project that combines elements of fortune, luck, and gaming. Players can join the community and participate in a variety of activities, such as participating in tournaments, competing against other players, and playing mini-games. The game also features a unique system of fortune and luck, where players can earn rewards and bonuses based on their performance. With its vibrant and engaging community, Makaneki-Nekos offers an exciting and rewarding experience for players of all ages.�
